snippet.title: V.Smile Game: Barney - The Land of Make Believe (2005 VTech)
snippet.description:
One day, Barney, BJ and Baby Bop find a book about a wonderful place called The Land of Make Believe, where a beautiful Princess lives in a royal fairy tale castle. Barney and his friends decide they would like to meet the Princess and become her friends, so they begin a journey to find her.
